(1) Setup Wordpress On Localhost
----------------------------------
==> Setup Xampp And Start [Apache , MySql]
==> Download Wordpress From [wordpress.org]
==> Take [wordpress] Folder After Extract And Set It In [htdocs] Folder
==> Then Run It In The Browser [localhost/wordpress] And Follow Instructions
==> When Prompt You To Enter [dbName , username , password , host] You Must Open Phpmyadmin And Create Database With Name That Give You
==> Enter username and pass of wordpress [username : magdy , password : @Bfci5555@]
